so report the discovery of resolved continuum\nemission associated with HD 34700B (projected separation $\\sim1850$AU), which\nwe explain through a circumstellar disk.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 Nov 2020 17:43:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-06"}
