ssion energy, cross-section, and lambda-corrected trap density.\nThis is important because of the intended use of beta-Ga2O3 in high-field\ndevices and the many orders of magnitude of possible doping.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 7 Nov 2020 01:54:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-03"}
